description:
8.64 asuperstop
Apply high order Butterworth band-stop filter.

The filter accepts the following options:
name: asuperstop

parameters.description: Set center frequency in Hertz. Allowed range is 2 to 999999. Default value is 1000.
parameters.name: centerf

parameters.description: Set filter order. Available values are from 4 to 20. Default value is 4.
parameters.name: order

parameters.description: Set Q-factor. Allowed range is from 0.01 to 100. Default value is 1.
parameters.name: qfactor

parameters.description: Set input gain level. Allowed range is from 0 to 2. Default value is 1.
parameters.name: level

source:
8.64 asuperstop

Apply high order Butterworth band-stop filter.

The filter accepts the following options:

centerf

Set center frequency in Hertz. Allowed range is 2 to 999999. Default value is 1000.

order

Set filter order. Available values are from 4 to 20. Default value is 4.

qfactor

Set Q-factor. Allowed range is from 0.01 to 100. Default value is 1.

level

Set input gain level. Allowed range is from 0 to 2. Default value is 1.
